#!/usr/bin/env ssc
---
name: std-ui-smoke-test
version: 1.0.0
description: Interpreter smoke test for std/ui/*.ssc — exercises every widget family, emits to a temp dir, prints smoke:ok.
backends: [int]
frontend: react
---

# std/ui smoke test

Exercises all ten `std/ui` widget modules in a single tree.
Run headless via the interpreter; asserts that `emit` completes without
throwing and that `println("smoke:ok")` is reached.

## Setup

[signal, setSignal, emit](std/ui/primitives.ssc)

[lower](std/ui/lower.ssc)

[defaultTheme](std/ui/theme.ssc)

[vstack, hstack, divider, spacer](std/ui/layout.ssc)

[heading, text](std/ui/typography.ssc)

[textField, checkbox, signalButton](std/ui/input.ssc)

[showWhen, signalText_, fragment_](std/ui/reactive.ssc)

[badge, spinner](std/ui/display.ssc)

[card, cardWithHeader, modal](std/ui/containers.ssc)

[tableCol, tableRow, table, sortableTable](std/ui/data.ssc)

[route, router, link](std/ui/routing.ssc)

## Signals

```scalascript
val counter     = signal("counter",   0)
val showModal   = signal("showModal", false)
val sortCol     = signal("sortCol",   "name")
val currentPath = signal("path",      "/home")
val name        = signal("name",      "Alice")
```

## Layout and Typography

```scalascript
val layoutSection = vstack(gap = 8)(
  heading(1, "std/ui smoke test"),
  heading(2, "Layout"),
  hstack(gap = 8)(
    text("left"),
    spacer(grow = true),
    text("right")
  ),
  divider()
)
```

## Input

```scalascript
val inputSection = vstack(gap = 8)(
  heading(2, "Input"),
  textField(value = name, label = "Name"),
  checkbox(checked = signal("agree", false), label = "Agree"),
  signalButton(counter, 1, "Click me"),
  signalButton(counter, 0, "Reset", disabled = true)
)
```

## Reactive

```scalascript
val reactiveSection = vstack(gap = 8)(
  heading(2, "Reactive"),
  showWhen(signal("flag", true), text("visible"), text("hidden")),
  signalText_(counter)
)
```

## Display

```scalascript
val displaySection = vstack(gap = 8)(
  heading(2, "Display"),
  badge("success", "success"),
  badge("3", "notification"),
  spinner()
)
```

## Containers

```scalascript
val containersSection = vstack(gap = 8)(
  heading(2, "Containers"),
  card(text("plain card")),
  cardWithHeader(heading(3, "Header"))(text("body")),
  modal(showModal, "Test Modal")(
    text("Modal body"),
    signalButton(showModal, false, "Close")
  )
)
```

## Data

```scalascript
val rows = List(
  tableRow(text("Alice"), text("30")),
  tableRow(text("Bob"),   text("25"))
)
val dataSection = vstack(gap = 8)(
  heading(2, "Data"),
  table(List(tableCol("Name", "name"), tableCol("Age", "age")), rows),
  sortableTable(sortCol, List(tableCol("Name", "name"), tableCol("Score", "score")),
    List(tableRow(text("Alice"), text("99")), tableRow(text("Bob"), text("88"))))
)
```

## Routing

```scalascript
val routingSection = vstack(gap = 8)(
  heading(2, "Routing"),
  hstack(gap = 8)(
    link("/home",  "Home",  currentPath),
    link("/about", "About", currentPath)
  ),
  router(currentPath, List(
    route("/home",  List(text("Home page"))),
    route("/about", List(text("About page")))
  ))
)
```

## Emit

```scalascript
val tree = vstack(gap = 24)(
  layoutSection,
  inputSection,
  reactiveSection,
  displaySection,
  containersSection,
  dataSection,
  routingSection
)

emit(lower(tree, defaultTheme), "/tmp/ssc-ui-smoke-test")
println("smoke:ok")
```
